- The Company has been presented the FICCI award 1999 - 2000 for 'Corporate initiatives in the field of rural developments'.
- Bharat Petroleum Corporation Ltd (BPCL) has launched yet another card product, SmartFleet, aimed at fleet owners and corporates.
- During 2000-01 the company issued bonus shares in the ratio of 1:1, thereby enhancing its equity capital to Rs 300 crore. Also Recently it acquired 55% stake in Kochi Refinery Limited (KRL) from the Government of India and 19% in Numaligarh Refinery Limited (NRL) from IBP.
The company has launched 'Smart fleet', a programme for fleet owners and corporates and the same received an enthusiastic response from over 2500 clients.
-The company has 'Petrocard', an customer loyalty programme, had enrolled over 2.25 lakh customers by theend of March 2001.
2001
