duction activities, Bharat Petroleum incorporated a wholly owned subsidiary called Bharat PetroResources Limited in 2006.KNOW MORE  International TradeAt BPCL, International Trade involves the import of crude oil, import and export of finished products, transportation of coastal product, risk management.KNOW MORE  Proficiency TestingTo cater to the needs of petroleum sector laboratories in and around India, Bharat Petroleum has launched Proficiency Testing labs.KNOW MORE        

		 

