A

SUMMER TRAINING REPORT 

ON

“ 

REQUIREMENTS OF L.P.G. GAS PRODUCT IN INDUSTRIES ANDBAZAAR (RETAIL) POTENTIAL ASSESMENT

 .” 

AT

BHARATPETROLEUMCORPORATION LTD.

JAIPUR, RAJASTHAN.PREPARED BY

RAMAN KUMAR JHA.

TAXILA BUSINESS SCHOOL MANSAROWAR JAIPUR.BATCH 2010-2012.UNDER THE GUIDANCE OF

 PROF. RAKHI ARORA. MR.SHISHIR KUMAR.(Assistant professor) (Territory manager)

 INTERNAL GUIDE. COMPANY GUIDE .

AS A PARTIAL FULFILLMENT PGDBM

PROGRAM 

OF T.B.S.

TAXILA BUSINESS SCHOOL

JAIPUR, RAJASTHAN.3
























 

