ABSTRACT.

SECTION 1

INTRODUCTION

1.1COMPANY PROFILE.

1.1. A. BRIEF AND HISTORY.1.1. B. ORGANISATIONAL STURTURE.1.1. C. MARKETING.1.1. D. FINANCE & ECONOMY.1.1. D. HUMAN RESOURCE.1.1. E. OPERATIONS.1.1. F. RESEARCH AND DEVELOPMENT.

1.2 INDUSTRY PROFILE. 

1.2. A. L.P.G. INDUSTRY1.2 L.P.G. INDUSTRIAL USES.1.2. B. BRIEF ABOUT THE COMPETITORS.

