OBJECTIVES, SCOPES, RESEARCH METHODOLOGY, DATA ANALYSIS,FINDINGS AND CONCLUSIONS

.

2.1. OBJECTIVE OF THE STUDY.2.2. SCOPES AND LIMITATION.2.3. RESEARCH METHODOLOGY.2.4. DATA ANALYSIS.2.4. A. INDUSTRY (BUSINESS-TO-BUSINESS).2.4. B. RETAIL MARKET (BAZAAR).2.5. FINDINGS.

